---
description: Do not use em dashes or en dashes in documentation prose.
globs: "**/*.md"
alwaysApply: true
---

When writing or editing documentation in this repo:

- Never use em dashes (`—`, U+2014) or en dashes (`–`, U+2013) in prose.
- Use commas, periods, semicolons, colons, or parentheses instead.
- Hyphen-minus (`-`) is fine for compound words, flags, and YAML keys.

Before finishing doc edits, search changed files for `—` and `–` and remove any matches.
